name: forever friends birthday card ♥
description:
These Birthday cards are handmade with stamps, pens and a number of embellishments to make them all different. Cards do say Happy Birthday on the front but are blank inside for your own message! All made with genuine Forever Friends stamps. Card measurements are 21 x 10 cm.

More can be made to order, please contact me for personal requirements!

name: winnie the pooh birthday cards
description:
Handmade with genuine Winnie the Pooh drawings, the collection if perfect for all ages! All cards are blank, if you would like any special message on the front then please contact me! Only a few available, cards can be made to order.

Disney logo is on the back of the cards for copyright purposes. Card measurements are 15 x 10.5 cm.

name: birthday boy football cards
description:
2 different designs, both embellished with footballs, trophies and shirts. Good for any age, made for birthdays but can be made for a different occasion if you need. Please contact me for any personal requirements for your cards.

Message inside - Happy Birthday!
Card measurements; card design 1 is 13.5 x 13.5 cm and card design 2 is 14.5 x 11 cm.

name: forever friends celebration card ♥
description:
Blank card, could be used for Birthday, Wedding or any other celebration! Only 1 available, more can be made to order, please e-mail me for any personal requirements. 

Handmade with genuine Forever Friends pictures, pale pink pearl drops and champagne embellishments. Card measures 21 x 10 cm.
